Summary
~~~~~~~
An Averath smoke shop has emerged in the marketplace.
Built in the center of the square the shack imports 
fine tobacco products into his shop.


ROOMS
~~~~~
Just one, the shop itself. It is where the merchant 
will be located


NPC
~~~
(20) Bilgan, the shopkeep

(20) Boogil, the handyman

Brothers who have lived together in Lloryk almost all 
of their lives. They deal with outside friendly druids
for all of their tobacco supplies.

OBJ
~~~
A fine seletion of smokables will be available to the 
public in this shop. And special cigars.


Treasure
~~~~~~~~

Just smokables and coffee at reasonable prices.